      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "FILE CONVERSION"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "File conversion allows files to be copied from one file format"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "to another, as determined by the SOURCE and DESTINATION profile"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "types.  During file conversion, a file is read in based upon"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "its SOURCE PROFILE characteristics, and is written out based"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "upon its DESTINATION PROFILE characteristics."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "If no PROFILE is specified, either SOURCE or DESTINATION, then"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the profile characteristics are determined by the profile that"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "corresponds to the file's extension."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "1+- For greater detail on the FILE CONVERSION function"
      },
      {
